  "title": "Part Time Service Crew (Marina Square)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Roles and Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Assist in handling and managing customer visit experience</li>\n  <li>Assist in crowd control and manage visitor safety</li>\n  <li>Assist in maintaining playground cleanliness &amp; its tidiness</li>\n  <li>Assist in managing the playground inventory and storage</li>\n  <li>Assist in operating &amp; upkeeping playground equipment</li>\n  <li>Support day to day admission check in/out process</li>\n  <li>Support day to day event activities and performance</li>\n  <li>Complete any other tasks assigned by the supervisor</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Our preferred candidate should meet the following requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Above 16 years old</li>\n  <li>Able to work on weekdays and have the flexibility to work shifts, weekends, and public/school holidays</li>\n  <li>At least GCE ‘N’ Level Certificate</li>\n  <li>A positive attitude and a strong commitment to ensuring customer satisfaction and ability to create a welcoming and friendly atmosphere infused with high energy and enthusiasm</li>\n  <li>Ability to work with young children and their families</li>\n  <li>Flexibility to work shifts, weekends, and public/school holidays</li>\n  <li>Capability to stand/walk for extended periods</li>\n  <li>Past experience in customer-facing roles is a plus</li>\n</ul>",
